item.title: Photography
item.description: Written by: Vipul People:“YOU SHOULD NOT BE MAKING PROMISES THAT YOU CANT KEEP BRUH”. I know, I know its been long since i posted anything because I had a lot of things happening in MINECRAFT, yeah thats true but I won’t be getting carried away by that now(I should write about minecraft someday tho). So as of now I have written a few posts (YAY for that), but most of them were related to programming and computer stuff , I thought why not make the blog a little interesting by talking about some basic photography(Everyone loves clicking good pics so keep reading).
